      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a reliable companion with plenty of heart? This vehicle is in fair condition and has been a steadfast partner on the road, showing some honest signs of its many adventures. While it has some cosmetic wear and could use a little TLC, it remains a solid, dependable ride ready for its next chapter with you!",
